post.description:
## Reference  
1. 参考接口 [转移拥有者](https://{{baseUrl}}/document/ukTMukTMukTM/uQzNzUjL0czM14CN3MTN)  


## Success Response Sample  
```
{
    "code": 0,
    "data": {
        "is_success": true,
        "meta_version": "0",
        "owner": {
            "member_id": "81b76f9f",
            "member_type": "userid"
        },
        "permission_version": "0",
        "token": "doccnJRfvXMX1UjLSAf8CxmcPLc",
        "type": "doc"
    },
    "msg": "Success"
}
```

text/plain.example:
{
    "type": "string",               // 文档类型 "doc" or "sheet" or "bitable" or "file"
    "token": "string",              // 文件的token
    "owner": {                      // 要转移到的新的文档所有者
         "member_type": "string",   // 用户类型，可选 email、openid、userid
         "member_id": "string"      // 用户类型下的值
    },
   "remove_old_owner": false,       // true 为转移后删除旧 owner 的权限，默认为false
   "cancel_notify": false           // true为不通知新owner，默认为false
}

